==English==
===Noun===
'''assault weapon''' 
[[Category:English nouns]]
# (''United States English'') A semi-automatic firearm similar in name, appearance, or design to a fully automatic firearm or military weapon.
# (''United States English'') A firearm that meets a set of conditions designated by law.
# (''United States English'') Any weapon employed in combat.
====Usage Note====
This term is considered to be pejorative by some. It is used primarily in a political context, and is rarely ascribed to weapons of military interest.